title: Part 1: Days 1-7
episode_desc: The Beatles arrive at Twickenham Studios and have three weeks to complete 14 new songs and a live show.
show_desc: Documentary about the music group The Beatles featuring in-studio footage that was shot in early 1969 for the 1970 feature film 'Let It Be.'

title: Part 2: Days 8-16
episode_desc: John, Paul and Ringo meet with George following his walkout and move the session to Apple Studios.
show_desc: Documentary about the music group The Beatles featuring in-studio footage that was shot in early 1969 for the 1970 feature film 'Let It Be.'

title: Part 3: Days 17-22
episode_desc: The Beatles must decide if they will perform live for the first time in three years.
show_desc: Documentary about the music group The Beatles featuring in-studio footage that was shot in early 1969 for the 1970 feature film 'Let It Be.'
